Package: freicoind
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - daemon
 Freicoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Freicoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Freicoin
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, freicoind, and the CLI tool
 freicoin-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: freicoin-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer network based digital currency - Qt GUI
 Freicoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Freicoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Freicoin
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides Freicoin-Qt, a GUI for Freicoin based on Qt.

Package: freicoin-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: peer-to-peer digital currency - standalone transaction tool
 Freicoin is an experimental new digital currency that enables instant
 payments to anyone, anywhere in the world. Freicoin uses peer-to-peer
 technology to operate with no central authority: managing transactions
 and issuing money are carried out collectively by the network. Freicoin
 is the name of the open source software which enables the use of this currency.
 .
 This package provides freicoin-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a freicoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
